title: The 137th sign of the Apocalypse
author: VD
content_html:
From Soccernet:

England have been overtaken by the United States in the FIFA Coca-Cola world rankings after dropping one place to eighth. The USA, still managed by Bruce Arena who guided his country to the quarter-finals of the 2002 World Cup, have reached their highest ever placing with a rise to sixth.

Heh heh heh….
